author: Ryan George Extra Plus!
description:
The world is getting weirder by the day. Florida is building robot bunnies to hunt snakes, toddlers are defeating cobras with their teeth, scientists are making rhinos radioactive, and chimps… well, chimps have decided butt fashion is in now. Oh, and pizza in Wisconsin is getting people high...by accident? … and somehow that’s just ONE week of news!

So yeah… it’s weird out there.
